Jack Cheatham https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jack_Cheatham 0 Jack Cheatham (December 28, 1894 – March 30, 1971) was an American character actor of the 1930s and 1940s. During his career he appeared in almost 200 films, with 100 of them being features. Jack_Cheatham ( December_28_,_1894 – March_30 , 1971 ) was an_American_character_actor of the_1930s_and_1940s .
